HEADWORD: Nuclear device
<hw>Nu"cle*ar dev"ice</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>an explosive
device, whether used as a weapon or for other purposes, which depends
for most of its explosive power on the release of energy from within
atomic nuclei. A <stype>fission device</stype> or a <stype>fusion
device</stype>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nuclear energy</ent>⟦br⟧
